main ls

List installed packages

USAGE:
    main ls [OPTIONS]

OPTIONS:
    -h, --help
            Show help message and exit.
    -V, --version
            Show version and exit.
        --completions <bash,zsh,fish>
            Generate shell completions.
    -a, --all
            Show all versions
        --json
            Output as JSON
